  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven or heavy pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add carrots, bell pepper, and ginger; cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add lamb and cook, breaking up with a spoon, until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add rice wine, curry powder, salt, and pepper; stir to coat lamb and vegetables.",
    "Add rice and stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20-25 minutes or until the liquid has been absorbed and the lamb is tender.",
    "Fluff pilaf with a fork and garnish with parsley."
